{
  "stem": "25114.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was always-- wanted to lift myself above the ordinary life, because it was pretty-- I grew up in the Great Depression.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's pretty tough on the kids that grew up in this particular time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just grew up exactly the particular time when that-- the Great Depression started, what, in 1929?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when I was ready to go to school only.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was all right, till the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very tough, living in Warsaw, and very, very hard conditions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Could you explain that further?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was little money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father, all of a sudden, started earning much less than he did, although he had work, because he was working for himself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was no opportunities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Great unemployment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the severe climate, it was-- you needed, you know, a lot to-- to keep you warm, good, warm clothes to keep you warm when winter came.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Harsh conditions.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And good food to nourish you to get through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was very scarce, everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there's no-- no way of-- very little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You just couldn't plan a future.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There's almost no future for young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They talk about here in Australia, but nothing like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was-- he had a work room with a partner to people employed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would make lots of mass-produced children's shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to get delivered the materials and everything, and they put it together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to export, or to ride around the country.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because most of the-- it was hand-- this was mass produced things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he was a maker of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the only trade when he was growing up, being a-- a scholar in Yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he was very learned in Jewish tradition.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
